/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, looking up towards the sky, giving a sense of grandeur to the scene. The street is lined with trees on both sides, their leaves a vibrant green against the backdrop of the clear blue sky. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades adding a splash of color to the scene. Cars are parked along the side of the road, hinting at the hustle and bustle of city life. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban landscapes. The image is bathed in the light of a sunny day, casting soft shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and trees.
